Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Briefe; Übersetzungen"

- Photos of Rubens' letters
- List of items in 'Rubens als Bürger' (dated 15.06.1967)
- Translations of Rubens' letters to Peter van Veen, Pierre Dupuy, Frederic de Marselaer and Peiresc (in german)
- Transcription of Marie Ruebbens' letter to Rubens (in german)
- Draft text: "Zum Buchtitel "Legatus" von dem berühmten Autor Herrn Marselaer, schloβherrn von Parck"
- Extracts from different publications
